            "title": "盤中速報 - 恆生科技指數上漲145.58點至4941.91點，漲幅3.04%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間06日11:04，恆生科技指數上漲145.58點（或3.04%），暫報4941.91點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-6.13%</li><li>近 1 月：-11.28%</li><li>近 3 月：-15.3%</li><li>近 6 月：-15.67%</li><li>今年以來：-13.05%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>地產代理概念領漲+4.00%。其中    方圓生活服務(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09978:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09978\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09978-HK</a>)            上漲        9.33%            ;        合富輝煌(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00733:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00733\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00733-HK</a>)            上漲        7.69%            ;        易居企業控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02048:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02048\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02048-HK</a>)            上漲        2.99%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>消費電子產品概念領漲+3.47%。其中    久融控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02358:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02358\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02358-HK</a>)            上漲        9.09%            ;        中國華星(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00485:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https:/